org.sxb.data.redis.support.atomic

クラス RedisAtomicInteger

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • org.sxb.data.redis.support.atomic.RedisAtomicInteger
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    java.io.Serializable, BoundKeyOperations<java.lang.String>

    public class RedisAtomicInteger
extends java.lang.Number
implements java.io.Serializable, BoundKeyOperations<java.lang.String>
    Atomic integer backed by Redis. Uses Redis atomic increment/decrement and watch/multi/exec operations for CAS operations.
    作成者:
    Costin Leau, Thomas Darimont
    関連項目:
    AtomicInteger, 直列化された形式

        public RedisAtomicInteger(java.lang.String redisCounter,
                          RedisConnectionFactory factory)

        factory - connection factory

      • RedisAtomicInteger

        public RedisAtomicInteger(java.lang.String redisCounter,
                          RedisOperations<java.lang.String,java.lang.Integer> template,
                          int initialValue)
        Constructs a new RedisAtomicInteger instance. Note: You need to configure the given template with appropriate RedisSerializer for the key and value. As an alternative one could use the RedisAtomicInteger(String, RedisConnectionFactory, Integer) constructor which uses appropriate default serializers.
        パラメータ:
        redisCounter - the redis counter
        template - the template
        initialValue - the initial value
